text: Kristian Jakobsson (born January 18, 1996) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Sparta Warriors of the GET-ligaen (SHL). Jakobsson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Modo Hockey during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Modo Hockey players Category:Mora IK players Category:Sparta Warriors players Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards
